request.description:
Adds a new school.

Expected success response (201):
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "School added successfully",
  "data": {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Green Valley High School",
    "address": "21 Main Street, Bangalore",
    "latitude": 12.9716,
    "longitude": 77.5946
  }
}

Returns all schools sorted by nearest distance from provided coordinates.

Expected success response (200):
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Schools fetched successfully",
  "data": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "name": "Green Valley High School",
      "address": "21 Main Street, Bangalore",
      "latitude": 12.9716,
      "longitude": 77.5946,
      "distanceKm": 4.912
    }
  ]
}
